org.activiti.workflow.simple.converter.step

接口 StepDefinitionConverter<U extends StepDefinition,T>

  • 所有已知实现类:
    BaseStepDefinitionConverter, ChoiceStepsDefinitionConverter, DelayStepDefinitionConverter, FeedbackStepDefinitionConverter, HumanStepDefinitionConverter, ParallelStepsDefinitionConverter, ScriptStepDefinitionConverter

    public interface StepDefinitionConverter<U extends StepDefinition,T>

    A class that is responsible for converting a single StepDefinition to all required artifacts needed.

    Please note that StepDefinitionConverter instances are reused and should be state-less.

    作者:
    Frederik Heremans
